data.value: Welcome to Kiwi's Co-Op Mod for Half-Life: Alyx! Ensure that Half-Life: Alyx uses these launch parameters: -console -vconsole -language english When starting KCOM, make sure that the VConsole window is not open. For help/support, please visit the Discord server linked in the "Help" menu above. Thank you for your interest in KCOM, enjoy! ===========================================================================================
